opencpn (2.5.0+dfsg-1) UNRELEASED; urgency=low

  * Packaged for upstream version 2.5.0
  * Drop most of TinyXML patch (superseded by upstream)
  * CSS and JavaScript cruft now dropped upstream
  * Move plugins into new opencpn-plugins package
  * Register docs with doc-base
  * Note what plugins dir should be if -plugins pkg is not installed
  * Suggests xtide and zygrib
  * Add DEP-5 comments to copyright file explaining embedded copies
  * Policy bumped to 3.9.3, without changes.
  * Compile main program with hardening flags and -fPIC.
  * Patch adding support for libgps20, backported from upstream 3.0.0 release.
  * Patch allowing hardening CFLAGS to make it through to plugin builds.
  * Closing ITP. (Closes: #538067)

  [ Anton Martchukov ]
  * Additional copyright file auditing

  [ Andreas Tille ]
  * Moved from SVN to Git

 -- M. Hamish Bowman <hamish_b@yahoo.com>  Sun, 16 Mar 2014 13:51:34 +1300

